Addon.name: Grow Your Own Dragon - Light Spark Edition
Addon.role: Do you have what it takes to grow your own dragon? All the way from an egg (once you rescue it from the dreaded Troll, Rock Monster or Lumberbad) to a baby to a fearsome troll-eating beast? We shall see about that.....

Addon.name: Dragon Mounts Addon
Addon.role: If you loved my aether dragon addon, then you will love this one! Dragon Mounts adds 17 new dragons, lots of new armor, and many new swords! Now you can have more fun in Minecraft!

Addon.name: Dragon Armor Addon (Spears Update)
Addon.role: Hello and welcome to the Dragon armor addon. This addon adds some items, swords and the main part of this addon: the Dragon armor. Its a strong armor that is stronger and has a higher durability than diamond. There is also obsidian armor and sword.

Addon.name: Dragon Add-On
Addon.role: Dragons! Everybody needs a pet dragon (or two) but you'll have to be brave and lucky! Mostly lucky I think. We have several types of dragons and a few unique dragon soldiers and wizards.

Addon.name: v2 Dragonborn Addon
Addon.role: Have you ever wanted skyrim in minecraft? Well, here it is! This is an addon that adds shouts, dragons, daedric lairs, dremora, and dragon lairs to the game to the game. There are 2 armor sets that include both bows and swords.

Addon.name: How To Train Your Dragon Add-on
Addon.role: HTTYD is an addon that introduces rideable dragons from the famous franchise 'How to train your dragon' to Minecraft, The addon is also combined with a script that allow a realistic flying behaviors. Unfortunately scripts are still exclusive to Windows 10, So I've provided a second behavior pack for other platforms that grants the old way of flying (by jumping and slowly falling).

Addon.name: Baby Ender Dragons Addon
Addon.role: This add-on implements a new dragon to the Overworld. An Ender Dragon would be way too overkill, but the baby of an Ender Dragon is certainly more fair. The spawn rate is quite low as it will only spawn in caves, but other than that their spawn pattern is quite hard to predict which makes it a fun and dangerous challenge.

Addon.name: Dragon Mounts Addon Beta
Addon.role: This add-on adds a bunch of cool dragons to your world. By installing this add-on you will be able to tame dragons, use them as flying mounts or get them to help you to take down your enemy.

Addon.name: Day of Dragons Add-on (Player Model) (1.14+ only)
Addon.role: The Day of Dragons Add-on will turn YOU into a 4D Dragon model with cool animations. It's like a dragon simulator which lets you become a cool dragon! Enjoy it!

Addon.name: Dark Dragon Addon
Addon.role: This add-on adds tamed and rideable winged dragons, these dark dragons have great strength and great speed in running and flying, and they protect you from monsters and help you in navigation and hunting. They are very wonderul !!

Addon.name: Dragon Brood
Addon.role: Do you want extra challenge to your survival world as you build yourself up to take on the Enderdragon?  The Enderdragon is willing to accommodate you!  She sends her Dragon Spawn Babies and her goons (or Dragoons) to pester you and just about any other mob around you. This Dragon Brood is pesky and can start spawning on you right after you spawn into your new world.

Addon.name: Aveo Dragon Addon
Addon.role: Too many dragons is not enough! We know that, you know that. Here's how we're helping: the Aveo Dragon. These long-necked, long-tailed, two-legged dragons of legend are here at last.

Addon.name: Aether Dragon Addon
Addon.role: Have you ever wanted a powerful pet aether dragon? If you do, then consider yourself lucky. I made it in Minecraft. This addon adds an Aether Dragon, one hostile, and one tamable. Be prepared though, it will be challenging to get a pet Aether Dragon.

Addon.name: Dragon Morph Addon
Addon.role: Ender Dragons are majestic creatures right? Wouldn't it be cool if you could become one. This addon makes it possible! Turning into one isn't going to be that easy though.

Addon.name: Curse Dragon
Addon.role: The curse Ender Dragon! It's just ender dragon but he's not look like normal ender dragon it has 3 heads and four wings And he can summon huge groups of lightning bolts!

Addon.name: Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Maid Addon (Unofficial)
Addon.role: Do you like Anime? This is a Minecraft recreation of one of Elon Musk's recommended animes.Summon a maid, transform it into a dragon and fly wth Tohru, Kanna, Elma, Lucoa! This add-on's based on 'Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Maid' by Coolkyousinnjya.

Addon.name: Dragon Ball Z Stands *NEW UPDATE*
Addon.role: My new dragon ball addon for minecraft mobile that adds stands like jojo's but dragon super that adds 9 characters in this version of the dragon ball addon.

Addon.name: Dragon Warboat
Addon.role: Be the Ruler of the Sea with your Dragon Warboat, and let loose with its Massive Crossbow. Mow down those mobs; you'll love it, they'll love it, everyone will love it.Shore bombardment anyone?

Map.name: BETA Dragon Run
Map.role: This map is the minigame dragon run which I made the map for (check for proof on channel). However there are still many things & I need to improve & change so this is a warning!!! I’m not perfect if it doesn’t work I’ll try to fix it, but I’m not promising anything.

Map.name: Dragon Hunter House

Map.role: Do you like bedwars and skywars? I like. This map is for training bridging skills. There are three modes: onestack, straight and andromeda. If you have some questions ask me. I'll answer your question. I hope you'll enjoy this map.

You can practice normal bridging, and staircase bridging, and now DIAGONAL BRIDGING! You spawn in the lobby, where you can choose what kind of bridging you will be doing!
